{"title_page": "Presenters of Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs", "text_new": "{{short description|Presenters of Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs}}\n\nThis list includes those who have acted as '''presenters of [[Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs]]'''. Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs is an annual [[music competition]] in [[Albania]] organised by the national broadcaster [[Radio Televizioni Shqiptar]] (RTSH). It determines the country's [[Albania in the Eurovision Song Contest|representative]] for the [[Eurovision Song Contest]] and has been broadcasting every year since its inauguration in 1962. \n\n== List of Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs presenters ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%; text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Edition\n! Hosts\n! Venue\n! Director\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1962\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 1\n| [[Margarita Xhepa]] and [[Luigj Gurakuqi Jr.]]\n| rowspan=\"7\" |[[:sq:Universiteti_i_Arteve,_Tiran\u00eb|ILA Venue]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[Luigj Gurakuqi Jr.]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1963\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 2\n| [[Vera Zheji]] and [[Skifter K\u00eblli\u00e7i]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1964\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 3\n| [[Drita Bardhi]] and [[Vangjel Heba]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1965\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 4\n| [[Drita Bardhi]] and [[Bujar Kapexhiu]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1966\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 5\n| [[Drita Bardhi]] and [[Bujar Kapexhiu]]\n| ?\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1967\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 6\n| [[Albert Minga]] and [[Drita Bardhi]]\n| ?\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1968\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 7\n| [[Drita Bardhi]] and [[Roland Trebicka]]\n| ?\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1969\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 8\n| [[Elisabeta Vasili]] and [[Ki\u00e7o Fotiadhi]]\n| rowspan=\"20\" | [[National Theatre of Opera and Ballet of Albania]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Albert Minga]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1970\n| Festivali i K\u00ebng\u00ebs 9\n| [[Adriana Fishta]] and [[Mevlan Shanaj]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n!1971\n| Fe